{"kanda":6,"sarga":50,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"अथोवाचमहातेजाहरिराजोमहाबलः ।किमियंव्यथितासेनामूढवातेवनौर्जले","trans":"Extremely brilliant and mighty Sugriva looking at the army of Vanaras said, \"Why are you worried like a boat tossed by wind in water?\"","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and now"},{"d":"महातेजाः","m":"extremely brilliant"},{"d":"महाबलः","m":"mighty"},{"d":"हरिराजः","m":"king of monkeys"},{"d":"वाच","m":"words"},{"d":"इयंसेना","m":"the army"},{"d":"जले","m":"by water"},{"d":"मूढवातेव","m":"tossed by wind"},{"d":"नौःइव","m":"like the boat"},{"d":"किम्","m":"why"},{"d":"व्यथिता","m":"worrying."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"सुग्रीवस्यवचश्श्रुत्वावालिपुत्रोऽङ्गदोऽब्रवीत् ।नत्वंपश्यसिरामंचलक्ष्मणंचमहारथम् शरजालचितौवीरावुभौदशरथात्मजौ ।शरतल्पेमहात्मानौशयानौरुधिरोक्षितौ","trans":"On hearing Sugriva's question, Angada the son of Vali said, \"Did you not see Dasaratha's sons Rama and chariot warrior Lakshmana, the great souls lying on a bed of arrows bathed in blood?\"","words":[{"d":"सुग्रीवस्य","m":"Sugriva's"},{"d":"वचः","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"वालिपुत्रः","m":"Vali's son"},{"d":"अङ्गदः","m":"Angada"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"},{"d":"शरजालचितौ","m":"network of arrows"},{"d":"रुधिरोक्षितौ","m":"bathed in blood"},{"d":"शरतल्पे","m":"on a bed of arrows"},{"d":"शयानौ","m":"lying"},{"d":"महात्मानौ","m":"great souls"},{"d":"दशरथात्मजौ","m":"Dasaratha's sons"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"महारथम्","m":"chariot warrior"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणंच","m":"Lakshmana also"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"नपश्यसि","m":"do you not see."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"सुग्रीवस्यवचश्श्रुत्वावालिपुत्रोऽङ्गदोऽब्रवीत् ।नत्वंपश्यसिरामंचलक्ष्मणंचमहारथम् शरजालचितौवीरावुभौदशरथात्मजौ ।शरतल्पेमहात्मानौशयानौरुधिरोक्षितौ","trans":"On hearing Sugriva's question, Angada the son of Vali said, \"Did you not see Dasaratha's sons Rama and chariot warrior Lakshmana, the great souls lying on a bed of arrows bathed in blood?\"","words":[{"d":"सुग्रीवस्य","m":"Sugriva's"},{"d":"वचः","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"वालिपुत्रः","m":"Vali's son"},{"d":"अङ्गदः","m":"Angada"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"},{"d":"शरजालचितौ","m":"network of arrows"},{"d":"रुधिरोक्षितौ","m":"bathed in blood"},{"d":"शरतल्पे","m":"on a bed of arrows"},{"d":"शयानौ","m":"lying"},{"d":"महात्मानौ","m":"great souls"},{"d":"दशरथात्मजौ","m":"Dasaratha's sons"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"महारथम्","m":"chariot warrior"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणंच","m":"Lakshmana also"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"नपश्यसि","m":"do you not see."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"अथाब्रवीद्वानरेन्द्रस्सुग्रीवःपुत्रमङ्गदम् ।नानिमित्तमिदंमन्येभवितव्यंभयेनतु","trans":"Then Vanara king Sugriva looking at Angada said, \"I do not think that the Vanaras running like this is not without any cause. Maybe out of fear of some reason ahead.\"","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"now"},{"d":"वानरेन्द्र","m":"Vanara king"},{"d":"सुग्रीवः","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"पुत्रम्","m":"son"},{"d":"अङ्गदम्","m":"Angada"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"said"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"अनिमित्तम्","m":"without any reason"},{"d":"नमन्ये","m":"not think"},{"d":"भयेन","m":"out of fear"},{"d":"भवितव्यम्","m":"some reason ahead."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"विषण्णवदनाह्येतेत्यक्तप्रहरणादिशः ।प्रपलायन्तिहरयस्त्रासादुत्फुल्ललोचनाः","trans":"\"Here, the distressed Vanaras with sad faces, their eyes downcast, are fleeing in all directions abandoning their arms.\"","words":[{"d":"अत्र","m":"in this place"},{"d":"एते","m":"their"},{"d":"हरयः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"त्रासात्","m":"distressed"},{"d":"उत्फुल्ललोचनाः","m":"downcast their eyes"},{"d":"त्यक्तप्रहरणाः","m":"abandoning arms"},{"d":"विषण्णवदनाः","m":"sad face"},{"d":"दिशः","m":"directions"},{"d":"प्रपलायन्ति","m":"fleeing."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"अन्योन्यस्यनलज्जन्तेनिरीक्षन्तिपृष्ठतः ।विप्रकर्षन्तिचान्योन्यंपतितंलङ्घयन्तिच","trans":"\"Without waiting to look back at others, not shy to see one another, the Vanaras are distancing themselves from those fallen and are seen fleeing.\"","words":[{"d":"अन्योन्यस्य","m":"one to the other"},{"d":"नलज्जन्ते","m":"not shy to see others"},{"d":"पृष्ठतः","m":"the other side"},{"d":"ननिरीक्षन्ति","m":"not waiting to look back at others"},{"d":"अन्योन्यम्","m":"one another"},{"d":"विप्रकर्षन्ति","m":"distancing"},{"d":"पतितम्","m":"fallen"},{"d":"लङ्घयन्तिच","m":"and fleeing."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"एतस्मिन्नन्तरेवीरोगदापाणिर्विभीषणः ।सुग्रीवंवर्धयामासराघवंचनिरैक्षत","trans":"In the meantime, heroic Vibheeshana holding mace came to Sugriva and Rama and cheered with victory.","words":[{"d":"एतस्मिन्","m":"in the mean"},{"d":"अन्तरे","m":"while"},{"d":"गदापाणिः","m":"holding mace"},{"d":"वीरः","m":"hero"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"सुग्रीवम्","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"विभीषणंच","m":"to Vibheeshana"},{"d":"राघवंच","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"निरैक्षत","m":"seeing"},{"d":"वर्धयामास","m":"cheered with victory."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"विभीषणंचसुग्रीवोदृष्टवावानरभीषणम् ।ऋक्षराजंमहात्मानंसमीपस्थमुवाचह","trans":"Beholding Vibheeshana, the Vanaras fled, said Sugriva to the great Jambavan who stood near him.","words":[{"d":"सुग्रीवः","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"वानरभीषणम्","m":"Vanaras beholding Vibheeshana"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"beholding"},{"d":"समीपस्थम्","m":"stood near"},{"d":"महात्मानम्","m":"great"},{"d":"ऋक्षराजम्","m":"king of Bears, Jambavan"},{"d":"उवाचह","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"विभीषणोऽयंसम्प्राप्तोयंदृष्टवावानरर्षभाः ।विद्रवन्तिपरितत्रसरावणात्मजशङ्कया","trans":"\"Vibheeshana has come here. Beholding him the foremost of the Vanaras fleeing suspecting him to be the son of Ravana.\"","words":[{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"सम्प्राप्तः","m":"having come here"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"beholding"},{"d":"वानरर्षभाः","m":"foremost Vanaras"},{"d":"रावणात्मशङ्काया","m":"thinking him to be Ravana's son"},{"d":"विद्रवन्ति","m":"suspecting"},{"d":"परित्रस्त","m":"fleeing."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"शीघ्रमेतान् सुसन्त्रस्तान्बहुधाविप्रधावितान् ।पर्यवस्थापयाख्याहिविभीषणमुपस्थितम्","trans":"\"Call them back who are running in different directions quickly. Tell them Vibheeshana has come here.\"","words":[{"d":"सुसन्त्रस्तान्","m":"fearing"},{"d":"बहुधा","m":"many directions"},{"d":"विप्रधावितान्","m":"fleeing"},{"d":"एतान्","m":"all of them"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"पर्यवस्था","m":"running"},{"d":"उपस्थितम्","m":"has come here"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"आख्याहि","m":"call them."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"सुग्रीवेणैवमुक्तस्तुजाम्बवानृक्षपार्थिवः ।वानरान्सान्त्वयामाससन्निरुध्यप्रधानतः","trans":"Sugriva having spoken in that way, the king of Bears, Jambavan restored the confidence of Vanaras.","words":[{"d":"सुग्रीवेण","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"having said"},{"d":"ऋक्षपार्थिवः","m":"king of Bears"},{"d":"जाम्बवान्","m":"Jambavan"},{"d":"प्रधानतः","m":"chief"},{"d":"वानरान्","m":"of Vanaras"},{"d":"निरुध्य","m":"restored"},{"d":"सान्त्वयामास","m":"confidence."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"तेनिवृत्ताःपुनःसर्वेवानरास्त्यक्तसम्भ्रमाः ।ऋक्षराजवचश्श्रुत्वातंचदृष्टवाविभीषणम्","trans":"Having heard Jambavan, all the Vanaras finally shed their fear and returned to see Vibheeshana.","words":[{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"तेवानराः","m":"the Vanaras"},{"d":"ऋक्षराजवचः","m":"Jambavan's words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"having heard"},{"d":"तम्","m":"their"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"beholding"},{"d":"त्यक्तसम्भ्रमाः","m":"finally shed their fear"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"again"},{"d":"विवृत्ताः","m":"returned."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"विभीषणस्तुरामस्यदृष्टवागात्रंशरैश्चितम् ।लक्ष्मणस्यचधर्मात्माबभूवव्यथितस्तदा","trans":"On seeing the body of Rama and Lakshmana fully covered by arrows, Vibheeshana also became piteous and sad.","words":[{"d":"धर्मात्मा","m":"righteous"},{"d":"विभीषणस्तु","m":"Vibheeshana also"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"चितम्","m":"mind"},{"d":"रामस्य","m":"Rama's"},{"d":"गात्रम्","m":"limbs"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणस्यच","m":"and Lakshmana's"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"observing"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"व्यथितः","m":"grievous"},{"d":"बभूव","m":"remained."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"जलक्लिन्नेनहस्तेनतयोर्नेत्रेप्रमृज्यच ।शोकसम्पीडितमनारुरोदविललापच","trans":"Vibheeshana, wetting his hands with water cleaned the eyes of Rama and Lakshmana. Tormented with pain he cried aloud.","words":[{"d":"जलक्लिन्नेन","m":"with water"},{"d":"हस्तेन","m":"in hand"},{"d":"तयोः","m":"their"},{"d":"नेत्रे","m":"eyes"},{"d":"प्रमृज्यच","m":"cleaned"},{"d":"शोकसम्पीडितमनाः","m":"tormented with pain"},{"d":"रुरोद","m":"aloud"},{"d":"विललापच","m":"cried."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"इमौतौसत्त्वसम्पन्नौविक्रान्तौप्रियसम्युगौ ।इमामवस्थांगमितौराक्षसैःकूटयोधिभिः","trans":"\"Both the princess, who are endowed with good nature, and power are fond of combat. The Rakshasas have reduced them to this state by their deceitful ways.\"","words":[{"d":"सत्त्वसम्पन्नौ","m":"endowed with good nature"},{"d":"विक्रान्तौ","m":"powerful"},{"d":"प्रियसम्युगौ","m":"fond of combat"},{"d":"तौ","m":"both"},{"d":"इमौ","m":"thus"},{"d":"कूटयोधिभिः","m":"deceitful"},{"d":"राक्षसैः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"इमाम्","m":"like this"},{"d":"अवस्थाम्","m":"predicament"},{"d":"गमितौ","m":"reduced to."}]},{"v":16,"dev":"भ्रातुःपुत्रेणमेतेनदुष्पुत्रेणदुरात्मना ।राक्षस्याजिह्मयाबुध्याचालितावृजुविक्रमौ","trans":"\"The princess who were guileless in their prowess were cheated by my evil minded and stupid son of my brother by his crooked thinking and cheating.\"","words":[{"d":"ऋजुविक्रमौ","m":"guileless in prowess"},{"d":"दुष्पुत्रेण","m":"stupid son"},{"d":"दुरात्मना","m":"evil minded"},{"d":"एतेन","m":"by him"},{"d":"भ्रातृपुत्रेण","m":"brother's son"},{"d":"राक्षस्या","m":"Rakshasa's"},{"d":"जिह्मया","m":"crooked"},{"d":"बुध्या","m":"mind"},{"d":"चालिता","m":"cheated."}]},{"v":17,"dev":"शरैरिमावलंविद्धौरुधिरेणसमुक्षितौ ।वसुधायामिमौसुप्तौदृश्येतेशल्यकाविव","trans":"\"Pierced with arrows, fully covered with blood, the bodies of the two princes appear like porcupines sleeping on the ground.\"","words":[{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"अलम्","m":"body"},{"d":"विद्धौ","m":"fully"},{"d":"रुधिरेण","m":"with blood"},{"d":"समुक्षितौ","m":"pierced with"},{"d":"वसुधायाम्","m":"on the ground"},{"d":"सुप्तौ","m":"sleeping"},{"d":"इमौ","m":"these two (Rama and Lakshmana)"},{"d":"शल्यकाविव","m":"like a porcupine"},{"d":"दृश्येते","m":"appears."}]},{"v":18,"dev":"ययोर्वीर्यमुपाश्रित्यप्रतिष्ठाकाङ्क्षितामया ।तावुभौदेहनाशायप्रसुप्तौपुरुषर्षभौ","trans":"\"These two bulls among men of great valour and fame whose refuge was sought by me are lying asleep wounded all over and limbs broken.\"","words":[{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"ययोः","m":"whose"},{"d":"वीर्यम्","m":"valour"},{"d":"आश्रित्य","m":"sought refuge"},{"d":"प्रतिष्ठा","m":"of great fame"},{"d":"काङ्क्षिता","m":"limbs broken"},{"d":"ता","m":"these"},{"d":"उभौ","m":"both"},{"d":"पुरुषर्षभौ","m":"bull among men"},{"d":"देहनाशाय","m":"wounded all over the body"},{"d":"प्रसुप्तौ","m":"lying asleep."}]},{"v":19,"dev":"जीवन्नद्यविपन्नोऽस्मिनष्टराज्यमनोरथः ।प्राप्तप्रतिज्ञश्चरिपुःसकामोरावणःकृतः","trans":"\"Having lost my life ambition for the kingdom, frustrated I am. My enemy Ravana, having succeeded in his vow, did this deed.\"","words":[{"d":"नष्टराज्यमनोरथः","m":"having lost kingdom"},{"d":"जीवन्नद्यअद्य","m":"life ambition"},{"d":"विपन्नः","m":"frustrated"},{"d":"अस्मि","m":"I am"},{"d":"रिपुः","m":"enemy"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"प्राप्तप्रतिज्ञः","m":"having succeeded in his vow"},{"d":"सकामश्च","m":"this deed"},{"d":"कृतः","m":"did."}]},{"v":20,"dev":"एवंविलपमानंतंपरिष्वज्यविभीषणम् ।सुग्रीवःसत्त्वसम्पन्नोहरिराजोऽब्रवीदिदम्","trans":"To Vibheeshana who was lamenting in that way, Sugriva, who was endowed with good qualities embraced him and spoke.","words":[{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"विलपमानम्","m":"lamenting in despair"},{"d":"तंविभीषणम्","m":"that Vibheeshana"},{"d":"परिष्वज्य","m":"embracing"},{"d":"सत्त्वसम्पन्नः","m":"endowed with good qualities"},{"d":"हरिराजः","m":"king of monkeys"},{"d":"सुग्रीवः","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":21,"dev