ः","m":"heroes हरिगणैः monkey army"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"them"},{"d":"लब्दसंज्ञौ","m":"on regaining consciousness"},{"d":"अरिन्दमौ","m":"tamers of their enemies"},{"d":"भ्रातरौ","m":"brothers"},{"d":"रामलक्ष्मणौ","m":"Rama and Lakshmana"},{"d":"गृह्य","m":"taking"},{"d":"किष्किन्धाम्","m":"to Kishkinda"},{"d":"गच्छ","m":"proceed."}]},{"v":25,"dev":"अहंतुरावणंहत्वासपुत्रंसहबान्धवम् ।मैथिलीमानयिष्यामिशक्रोनष्टामिवश्रियम्","trans":"\"On killing Ravana and his sons along with his kin, I will on my part also bring Mythili just as Indra recovered his prosperity.\"","words":[{"d":"अहंतु","m":"I also"},{"d":"सपुत्रम्","m":"his sons"},{"d":"सहबान्दवम्","m":"with the kin"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"हत्वा","m":"having killed"},{"d":"शक्रः","m":"Indra"},{"d":"नष्टाम्","m":"loss"},{"d":"श्रियमिव","m":"prosperity"},{"d":"मैथिलीम्","m":"Mythili also"},{"d":"आनयिष्यामि","m":"will bring."}]},{"v":26,"dev":"श्रुत्वैतद्वानरेन्द्रस्यसुषेणोवाक्यमब्रवीत् ।दैवासुरंमहद्युद्धमनुभूतंसुदारुणम्","trans":"Hearing the words of Vanara Lord, Sushena spoke about the fierce and great war that he had experienced between Devas and asuras.","words":[{"d":"वानरेन्द्रस्य","m":"Vanara Lord"},{"d":"एतत् वाक्यम्","m":"these words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"सुषेणः","m":"Sushena"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"},{"d":"दैवासुरम्","m":"Devatas and Asuras"},{"d":"सुदारुणम्","m":"fierce"},{"d":"महत्","m":"great"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"in war"},{"d":"अनुभूतम्","m":"experienced."}]},{"v":27,"dev":"तदास्मदानवाशरसम्स्पर्शकोविदाः ।निजघ्नुश्शस्त्रविदुषश्चादयन्तोमुहुर्मुहुः","trans":"\"Then the Rakshasas adept in using arms went about agitating concealing themselves, attacking Devatas who were learned in using arms.\"","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"शरसम्स्पर्शकोविदाः","m":"adept in using arms"},{"d":"दानवाः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"शस्त्रविदुषः","m":"learned in using arms"},{"d":"देवान्","m":"Devatas"},{"d":"मुहुर्मुहुः","m":"again and again"},{"d":"छादयन्तः","m":"concealing by tricks"},{"d":"निजघ्नुः